From bf9a2912cf49a959d1f20da9d1221e98f9dc2304 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Phil Edworthy <phil.edworthy@renesas.com>
Date: Tue, 19 Jan 2021 15:18:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 17/70] arm64: dts: Add Salvator-XS cr7_rproc

This adds support for H3, M3 and M3N Salvator-XS boards.
The RVGC virtual display is set to 800x600, located in the centre of a 1920x720 display.
This is chosen for a good demo using the 2D-WOW CR7 application.
